    "| 3. **Consistency** | Are values coherent? | Do related fields align? Are formats standardized? |\n",
    "| 4. **Accuracy** | Do values reflect reality? | Do entries match verified sources? Are timestamps reliable? |\n",
    "\n",
    "Each level must be strong before building the next. I'm using a pyramid thinking where completeness is the foundation."
